  "body": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en-US\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<title>ERDDAP - CAGES Alabama Data - Make A Graph</title>\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"https://gcoos4.geos.tamu.edu/erddap/images/favicon.ico\">\n<link href=\"https://gcoos4.geos.tamu.edu/erddap/images/erddap2.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n<link rel=\"alternate\" type=\"application/rss+xml\" \n  href=\"https://gcoos4.geos.tamu.edu/erddap/rss/CAGES_Alabama.rss\" \n  title=\"ERDDAP: CAGES Alabama Data\">\n\n</head>\n<body>\n<table class=\"compact nowrap\" style=\"width:100%; background-color:#128CB5;\">\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"text-align:center; width:80px;\"><a rel=\"bookmark\"\n      href=\"https://gcoos.org\"><img\n      title=\"Gulf of America Coastal Ocean Observing System\"\n      src=\"https://gcoos4.geos.tamu.edu/erddap/images/gcoosb.png\" alt=\"GCOOS\" width=\"155\"\n      style=\"vertical-align:middle;\"></a></td>\n    <td style=\"text-align:left; font-size:x-large; color:#FFFFFF; \">\n      <strong>Biological and Socioeconomics</strong>\n      <br>\n      </td>\n    <td style=\"text-align:right; font-size:small;\">\n       &nbsp; &nbsp;\n      <br>Brought to you by\n      <a title=\"National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration\" rel=\"bookmark\"\n      href=\"https://www.noaa.gov\">NOAA</a>\n      <a title=\"National Marine Fisheries Service\" rel=\"bookmark\"\n      href=\"https://www.fisheries.noaa.gov\">NMFS</a>\n      <a title=\"Southwest Fisheries Science Center\" rel=\"bookmark\"\n      href=\"https://swfsc.noaa.gov\">SWFSC</a>\n      <a title=\"Environmental Research Division\" rel=\"bookmark\"\n      href=\"https://swfsc.noaa.gov/textblock.aspx?Division=ERD&amp;id=1315&amp;ParentMenuId=200\">ERD</a>\n      &nbsp; &nbsp;\n      </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n<!-- Big HTML tooltips are generated with wz_tooltip from \n    http://wztip.info/index.php/Main_Page (LGPL license) -->\n<script src=\"https://gcoos4.geos.tamu.edu/erddap/images/wz_tooltip.js\"></script>\n\n<div class=\"standard_width\">\n\n<h1 class=\"nowrap\"><a title=\"Click here to return to the ERDDAP home page.\" \nrel=\"start\" href=\"https://gcoos4.geos.tamu.edu/erddap/index.html\">ERDDAP</a>\n &gt; <a rel=\"contents\" href=\"https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;gcoos4&#x2e;geos&#x2e;tamu&#x2e;edu&#x2f;erddap&#x2f;tabledap&#x2f;index&#x2e;html&#x3f;page&#x3d;1&#x26;itemsPerPage&#x3d;1000\">tabledap</a>\n &gt; Make A Graph\n<img src=\"https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;gcoos4&#x2e;geos&#x2e;tamu&#x2e;edu&#x2f;erddap&#x2f;images&#x2f;QuestionMark&#x2e;jpg\" alt=\"&#x3f;\" onmouseover=\"Tip('<div class=&quot;standard_max_width&quot;><strong>To make a graph of data from this tabular dataset, repeatedly:</strong><ol> <li>Change the &quot;Graph Type&quot; and the variables for the graph\\&#39;s axes. <li>Change the &quot;Constraints&quot; to specify a subset of the data. <li>Change the &quot;Graph Settings&quot; as desired. <li>Press &quot;Redraw the Graph&quot;. </ol> This Make A Graph web page just simplifies the creation of tabledap URLs with graphics commands. <br><strong>If you want, you can create these URLs by hand or have a computer program do it.</strong> <br>Then you don\\&#39;t have to use this form to get data. See the &quot;Bypass this form&quot; link below.</div>')\" onmouseout=\"UnTip()\"  >\n\n</h1>\n<table class=\"compact nowrap\">\n  <tr>\n    <td>Dataset Title:&nbsp;</td>\n    <td style=\"vertical-align:middle\"><span class=\"standoutColor\" style=\"font-size:130%; line-height:130%;\"><strong>CAGES Alabama Data</strong>\n      <a rel=\"alternate\" \n  href=\"https://gcoos4.geos.tamu.edu/erddap/subscriptions/add.html?datasetID=CAGES_Alabama&amp;showErrors=false&amp;email=\" \n  title=\"\"><img alt=\"Subscribe\"\n    title=\"Get&#x20;an&#x20;email&#x20;immediately&#x20;whenever&#x20;this&#x20;dataset&#x20;changes&#x2e;&#x2e;&#x2e;\" \n    src=\"https://gcoos4.geos.tamu.edu/erddap/images/envelope.gif\" ></a>\n      <a rel=\"alternate\" type=\"application/rss+xml\"   href=\"https://gcoos4.geos.tamu.edu/erddap/rss/CAGES_Alabama.rss\" \n  title=\"\"><img alt=\"RSS\"\n    title=\"Subscribe to the RSS feed for this dataset...\" \n    src=\"https://gcoos4.geos.tamu.edu/erddap/images/rss.gif\" ",
